Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.itinfrastructure.events

Class ITInfrastructureOutTopicEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.itinfrastructure.events.ITInfrastructureOutTopicEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class ITInfrastructureOutTopicEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    ITInfrastructureOutTopicEvent provides the structure of the IT Infrastructure OMAS's OutTopic events. The values for elements and their classifications come from the events. They are not guaranteed to be current. If the latest values are required, the element should be queried from the repository using its GUID. The event values are useful if the third party catalog needs to maintain an exact record of all the versions.
